snippet.description:
You are the widowed Mother of four children living on a farm in 18th Century Europe. 

War has brought famine.  Your goal is not to starve. 

Each day you send your children to farm, mine, or hunt to feed the family;
buy what you can afford at the market;
welcome your children home at night;
and feed them, if you can.

Depending on your decisions, you might survive. But at what cost?

A LowRezJam2022 entry, made for PlayDate using the Pulp Engine. Download for free at:
https://coronavitae.itch.io/starvation-simulator-for-playdate

